summary: The test suite provides unit tests for graph neural network model implementations in the DGLGO library, checking that each model can be instantiated, executed on sample graphs, and produce outputs without errors. It also includes placeholder test functions for various graph and node prediction pipeline components that are currently inactive.
business_intent: Validate the correctness and stability of GNN model code to prevent regressions and ensure that new changes do not break model construction or forward passes, while laying groundwork for future pipeline testing.
